{
  "stem": "11882.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her son, by the way, they went eventually to Alaska.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She's from Western New York, you know, with me-- college classmate and so forth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she became a very excellent German language professor for Western New York.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did TV presentations.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A very successful teaching career.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She finally got her teaching job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And later went to Florida, where-- after her parents had died, and she had bad rheumatism, and she and her husband went-- where unfortunately he died.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then the son-- a lawyer, too-- had gotten a job as Assistant District Attorney in Alaska.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Ingemaus, in order to be close to her son, pulled herself up from Florida, and built a home in-- she wanted to come here, but she couldn't quite make it-- up in Juneau, Alaska.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she lectures on Nuremberg among the Alaskan to the Alaskan lawyers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we hope to meet in September.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She's coming down for our-- turn off your TV-- 60th college anniversary meeting.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Directly in Nuremberg, there was no sense of being treated in any way but royally-- very, very nicely.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were examined, and your examination was what counted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They picked out their interpreters on ability.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Our Napoleon, Colonel Dostert, it didn't interest him in the least whether you were 18, or 75, or what you were-- or a woman, or a man, or a Czech, or a Frenchmen, or a one-time Russian, or an American.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A woman or man played no role.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I would think-- I can't say this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can't really say this with any authority.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It is not impossible that the majority of these key employees in the interpreting-- the trial interpreting-- may have been women.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm not sure of that, though.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Don't think of that as a check down figure.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
